#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Sissejuhatus"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&dolphin; is &plasma;'s default file manager. It aims to improve usability "
"at the user interface level. &dolphin; focuses only on being a file manager "
"whereas &konqueror;, which was &kde;'s default file manager in &kde; 3 and "
"can still be used for file management, is a universal viewer for many file "
"types."
msgstr ""
"&dolphin; on &plasma; vaikimisi failihaldur, mille eesmärk on pakkuda "
"kasutajale failide võimalikult hõlpsa ja mugava haldamise võimalust. "
"&dolphin; keskendub ainult failide haldamisele, samas kui &kde; 3 vaikimisi "
"failihaldur &konqueror; on väga paljude failitüüpide universaalne näitaja. "
"Nii on arendajatel olnud võimalik koondada oma tähelepanu just "
"kasutajaliidesele, et see sobiks võimalikult hästi just failide haldamise "
"nõuetega."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This design approach allows the developers to concentrate on optimizing the "
"user interface for the specific task of file management."
msgstr ""
"Nii on arendajatel olnud võimalik koondada oma tähelepanu eriti "
"kasutajaliidesele, et see sobiks võimalikult hästi just failide haldamise "
"nõuetega."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please report any problems or feature requests to the &dolphin; author via "
"the bug report dialog. This is accessible either from the "
"<guibutton>Control</guibutton> button at the right of the toolbar in the "
"default mode without menubar; or from <menuchoice><guimenu>Help</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Report Bug...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu of the "
"application, if the menubar is shown."
msgstr ""
"Palun anna kõigist probleemidest või uute omaduste soovidest teada &dolphin;"
"i autorile vigadest teatamise dialoogi kaudu. Selle saab avada rakenduse "
"vaikimisi menüüribata välimuse puhul tööriistariba paremas servas asuva nupu "
"<guibutton>Juhtimine</guibutton> alt või menüükäsuga "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Abi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Saada vearaport...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, kui menüüriba peaks olema nähtaval."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &dolphin;"
msgstr "&dolphin;i kasutamine"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid "&dolphin; User Interface"
msgstr "&dolphin;i kasutajaliides"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid "The screenshot below shows &dolphin;'s default user interface:"
msgstr "Pildil näeb &dolphin;i vaikimisi kasutajaliidest:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of &dolphin;'s default user interface"
msgstr "&dolphin;i vaikimisi kasutajaliides"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&dolphin;'s default user interface.</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&dolphin;i vaikimisi kasutajaliides.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>&dolphin;'s default user interface.</para>"
msgstr "<para>&dolphin;i vaikimisi kasutajaliides.</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid "The elements of the default user interface are:"
msgstr "Vaikimisi kasutajaliides koosneb järgmistest elementidest:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The toolbar, which can be used for quick access to frequently used actions. "
"The toolbar can be customized by clicking it with the &RMB; and choosing "
"<menuchoice><guimenuitem>Configure Toolbars...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"from the context menu, with <guimenuitem>Configure Toolbars...</guimenuitem> "
"from the <guibutton>Control</guibutton> button at the right of the toolbar "
"or via <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure "
"Toolbars...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> from the main menu."
msgstr ""
"Tööriistariba, mis võimaldab kiiresti kasutada sagedamini vaja minevaid "
"toiminguid. Tööriistariba saab kohandada, kui klõpsata sellele &HPNga; ja "
"valida kontekstimenüüst <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Tööriistaribade "
"seadistamine...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, käsuga "
"<guimenuitem>Tööriistaribade seadistamine...</guimenuitem> tööriistariba "
"paremal servas asuva nupu <guibutton>Juhtimine</guibutton> alt või kasutades "
"menüükäsku <menuchoice><guimenu>Seadistused</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Tööriistaribade seadistamine...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:156 index.docbook:267 index.docbook:297
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of &dolphin;'s toolbar"
msgstr "&dolphin;i tööriistariba"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid "The default toolbar."
msgstr "Vaikimisi tööriistariba."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:165
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toolbar items where the icon is sufficient for knowing the command do not "
"have text alongside the icons. This can be changed by a &RMB; click and "
"selecting the item text below <guilabel>Show Text</guilabel>. The "
"<guibutton>Control</guibutton> button at the right side of the toolbar is "
"only displayed if the menubar is hidden."
msgstr ""
"Tööriistariba elementidel, mille puhul ikoonist piisab käsu mõistmiseks, ei "
"ole ikooni kõrval teksti. Seda saab muuta, kui klõpsata &HPNga; ja valida "
"<guilabel>Näita teksti</guilabel>. Tööriistariba paremal servas asuvat nuppu "
"<guibutton>Juhtimine</guibutton> näeb ainult siis, kui menüüriba on peidetud."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The location bar, which always displays the path to the current folder. It "
"can be switched between two different modes, see the <link linkend="
"\"location-bar\">section on the location bar</link> for details."
msgstr ""
"Asukohariba, mis näitab alati aktiivse kataloogi asukohta. Sellel on kaks "
"režiimi, mida tutvustab põhjalikumalt <link linkend=\"location-bar\">vastav "
"osa</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <link linkend=\"dolphin-view\">view</link>, which shows all files and "
"folders in the current folder."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"dolphin-view\">Vaade</link>, mis näitab kõiki aktiivse "
"kataloogi faile ja katalooge."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <link linkend=\"places-panel\"><guilabel>Places</guilabel> panel</link>, "
"which provides quick access to bookmarked locations and disks or other media."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"places-panel\"><guilabel>Asukohtade</guilabel> paneel</"
"link>, mis tagab kiire ligipääsu järjehoidjatesse pandud asukohtadele ning "
"plaatidele ja muudele andmekandjatele."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:191
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If desktop search and file indexing are enabled in the <guilabel>Desktop "
#| "Search</guilabel> module in the &systemsettings; the panel provides "
#| "<guilabel>Recently Saved</guilabel> items and allows you to search for "
#| "<guilabel>Documents</guilabel>, <guilabel>Images</guilabel>, "
#| "<guilabel>Audio Files</guilabel> and <guilabel>Video</guilabel>."
msgid ""
"If desktop search and file indexing are enabled in the <guilabel>Desktop "
"Search</guilabel> module in the &systemsettings; the panel provides "
"<guilabel>Recent</guilabel> items and allows you to search for "
"<guilabel>Documents</guilabel>, <guilabel>Images</guilabel>, <guilabel>Audio "
"Files</guilabel> and <guilabel>Video</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Kui Süsteemi seadistuste moodulis <guilabel>Töölauaotsing</guilabel> on "
"töölauaotsing ja failide indekseerimine lubatud, näitab paneel "
"<guilabel>viimati salvestatud</guilabel> elemente ning lubab otsida "
"<guilabel>dokumente</guilabel>, <guilabel>pilte</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>helifaile</guilabel> ja <guilabel>videoid</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:197
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The status bar. It displays the name, size and type of the file which is "
"currently hovered over with the mouse, or the number and size of the files "
"which are selected. At the right, there is a zoom slider that allows you to "
"adjust the size of the icons in the view."
msgstr ""
"Olekuriba, mis näitab faili nimine, suurust ja tüüpi, mille kohal viibib "
"parajasti hiir, või valitud failide arvu ja suurust. Paremal paikneb "
"suurendusliugur, mis võimaldab muuta vaate ikoonide suurust."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The menubar (hidden by default), which provides access to all commands and "
"configuration options. See the <link linkend=\"commands-menubar\">Command "
"Reference</link> for a list of all menu commands. The menubar can be toggled "
"with <guimenuitem>Show Menubar</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;<keycap>M</keycap></keycombo>) from the <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"menu or the <guibutton>Control</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Menüüriba (vaikimisi peidetud), mis võimaldab kasutada kõiki käske ja "
"seadistamisvalikuid. Kõik menüükäsud leiab osast <link linkend=\"commands-"
"menubar\">Käskude seletused</link>. Menüüriba näitamist saab lülitada kas "
"käsuga <guimenuitem>Menüüriba näitamine</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>M</keycap></keycombo>), mille leiab menüüst "
"<guimenu>Seadistused</guimenu> või nupu <guibutton>Juhtimine</guibutton> alt."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the menubar is hidden, all its actions are available from the "
"<guibutton>Control</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Kui menüüriba on peidetud, saab kõiki selle toiminguid kasutada nupu "
"<guibutton>Juhtimine</guibutton> alt."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:215
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The additional <guilabel>Information</guilabel>, <guilabel>Folders</"
"guilabel> and <guilabel>Terminal</guilabel> panels are hidden by default, "
"for more information see <link linkend=\"panels\"><guilabel>Panels</"
"guilabel>.</link>"
msgstr ""
"Täiendavad paneelid <guilabel>Info</guilabel>, <guilabel>Kataloogid</"
"guilabel> ja <guilabel>Terminal</guilabel> on vaikimisi peidetud. Vaata "
"lähemalt osa <link linkend=\"panels\"><guilabel>Paneelid</guilabel></link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:228
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &dolphin; View"
msgstr "&dolphin;i vaade"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using the View"
msgstr "Vaate kasutamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The view displays all files and folders in the current folder. These items "
"can be accessed or manipulated in different ways:"
msgstr ""
"Vaade näitab kõiki aktiivse kataloogi faile ja katalooge. Neid saab kasutada "
"mitmel moel:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:239
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "A file or folder can be opened by clicking it with the &LMB; (or double-"
#| "clicking, if <guilabel>Double-click to open files and folders</guilabel> "
#| "is enabled in the <link linkend=\"preferences-dialog-navigation"
#| "\"><quote>Navigation</quote> section of the settings</link>)."
msgid ""
"A file or folder can be opened by clicking it with the &LMB; (or double-"
"clicking, if <guilabel>Open by double-clicking instead</guilabel> is enabled "
"in the &systemsettings; in the <menuchoice><guimenu>Workspace</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>General Behavior</guimenuitem></menuchoice> module)."
msgstr ""
"Faili või kataloogi saab avada sellele &HVNga; klõpsates (või topeltklõpsu "
"tehes, kui <link linkend=\"preferences-dialog-navigation\">seadistusdialoogi "
"kaardil <quote>Liikumine</quote></link> on sisse lülitatud valik "
"<guilabel>Failide ja kataloogide avamine topeltklõpsuga</guilabel>)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:246
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking any item or the white area around the items with the &RMB; opens a "
"context menu which provides access to many frequently used actions for the "
"item or the current folder, respectively."
msgstr ""
"Mõnele elemendile või elementide kõrval asuvale valgele alale &HPNga; "
"klõpsates avaneb kontekstimenüü, mis pakub sagedamini vajaminevaid "
"toiminguid vastavalt elemendi või aktiivse kataloogi jaoks."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:252
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the &LMB; is pressed on an item, but not immediately released, the item "
"can be dragged and dropped in another folder in the current view or in "
"another &dolphin; view (in another &dolphin; window or in the same window if "
"the view is split, see below) to move or copy it or to create a symbolic "
"link. Items can even be dropped in another application to open them in that "
"application."
msgstr ""
"Kui elemendile klõpsata &HVNga;, aga nuppu mitte kohe lahti lasta, saab "
"elementi lohistada mõnda aktiivse vaate teise kataloogi või ka &dolphin;i "
"teise vaatesse (teises &dolphin;i aknas või samas aknas, kui vaade on "
"poolitatud, millest kõneldakse allpool) ja seda sel moel liigutada või "
"kopeerida või luua nimeviit. Elemente võib lohistada isegi teise rakendusse, "
"et neid seal avada."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:261
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&dolphin; remembers the history of visited folders. To navigate backward or "
"forward in the history, the corresponding buttons in the toolbar can be used:"
msgstr ""
"&dolphin; jätab meelde külastatud kataloogide ajaloo. Ajaloos edasi või "
"tagasi liikumiseks saab kasutada vastavaid tööriistariba nuppe."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:273
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Back and Forward buttons in the toolbar."
msgstr "Tööriistariba edasi- ja tagasiliikumise nupud."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:276
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>Back</guibutton> and <guibutton>Forward</guibutton> buttons "
"in the toolbar can be used to navigate in the history."
msgstr ""
"Tööriistariba nuppudega <guibutton>Tagasi</guibutton> ja <guibutton>Edasi</"
"guibutton> saab liikuda ajaloos."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:284
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you click with the &MMB; the item in the history is opened in a new tab "
"thus keeping the current tab with its content."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:290
#, no-c-format
msgid "&dolphin; View Appearance"
msgstr "&dolphin;i vaate välimus"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid "The toolbar contains buttons to control the appearance of the view:"
msgstr "Tööriistaribal leiduvad nupud, millega saab määrata vaate välimust:"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:303
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>The buttons in the toolbar which control the appearance of the view."
"</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Tööriistariba vaate välimust määravad nupud.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:305
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<para>The buttons in the toolbar which control the appearance of the view.</"
"para>"
msgstr "<para>Tööriistariba vaate välimust määravad nupud.</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:311
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "All the settings discussed below and other options concerning, &eg; the "
#| "sorting of the files in the current folder, can also be modified in the "
#| "<guimenu>View</guimenu> menu and in the <link linkend=\"view-properties-"
#| "dialog\">View Properties dialog</link>. By default, these settings are "
#| "remembered for each folder separately. This behavior can be changed in "
#| "the <link linkend=\"preferences-dialog-general\"><quote>General</quote></"
#| "link> section of the settings."
msgid ""
"All the settings discussed below and other options concerning, &eg; the "
"sorting of the files in the current folder, can also be modified in the "
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> menu and in the <link linkend=\"view-properties-"
"dialog\">View Display Style dialog</link>. By default, these settings are "
"remembered for each folder separately. This behavior can be changed in the "
"<link linkend=\"preferences-dialog-general\"><quote>General</quote></link> "
"section of the settings."
msgstr ""
"Kõiki allpool käsitletud seadistusi ning muid asjakohaseid valikuid, näiteks "
"failide sortimist aktiivses kataloogis, saab muuta ka menüüga "
"<guimenu>Vaade</guimenu> ja <link linkend=\"view-properties-dialog\">vaate "
"omaduste dialoogis</link>. Vaikimisi jäetakse need seadistuste iga kataloogi "
"kohta eraldi meelde. Seda käitumist saab muuta seadistustedialoogi <link "
"linkend=\"preferences-dialog-general\"><quote>üldiste</quote> seadistuste</"
"link> osas."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:322 index.docbook:1222
#, no-c-format
msgid "View Modes"
msgstr "Vaaterežiimid"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:324
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The first three buttons in the above screenshot switch between &dolphin;'s "
"view modes."
msgstr ""
"Esimesed kolm nuppu pildil võimaldavad lülitada &dolphin;i vaaterežiimide "
"vahel."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:330
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <guibutton>Icons</guibutton> view, which is the default, files will "
"be represented by an icon that visualizes the file type, and a folder icon "
"will be shown for subfolders. The names of folders and files, and the items "
"enabled in <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Additional "
"Information</guisubmenu></menuchoice>, are displayed below the icons."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Ikoonivaates</guibutton>, mis on vaikimisi vaade, tähistavad "
"faile ikoonid, mis erinevad vastavalt failide tüübile, ning alamkataloogide "
"puhul näidatakse kataloogiikooni. Kataloogide ja failide nimesid ning "
"teavet, mis on lubatud alammenüüs <menuchoice><guimenu>Vaade</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Lisateave</guisubmenu></menuchoice>, näidatakse ikoonide "
"all."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:338
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Compact</guilabel> view shows the folder contents as icons "
"with the name beside it and the items enabled in <menuchoice><guimenu>View</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Additional Information</guisubmenu></menuchoice> below "
"the name. The items are grouped in columns similar to the <guilabel>Short "
"View</guilabel> in the &kde; file dialog."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Kompaktne</guilabel> vaade näitab kataloogide sisu ikoonidena, "
"mille kõrval on nimi ja selle all teave, mis on lubatud alammenüüs "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Vaade</guimenu><guisubmenu>Lisateave</guisubmenu></"
"menuchoice>. Elemendid on rühmitatud veergudesse nagu &kde; failidialoogi "
"<guilabel>lühivaate</guilabel> korral."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:346
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <guibutton>Details</guibutton> view, the folder contents are "
"displayed as a detailed list which contains the name, size and last "
"modification time of each item. Additional columns can be added by clicking "
"a column header with the &RMB;."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Üksikasjade</guibutton> vaates näidatakse kataloogide sisu "
"üksikasjaliku loendina, mis sisaldab iga elemendi nime, suurust ja viimase "
"muutmise aega. Klõpsates veerupäisele &HPNga;, saab lisada muidki veerge."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:352
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "In the context menu of the header line you can choose between custom or "
#| "automatic column width. Automatic width adjusts the width of all columns "
#| "once to display the longest item in the column completely, except for the "
#| "<guilabel>Name</guilabel> column where the extension is replaced by "
#| "<quote>...</quote>"
msgid ""
"In the context menu of the header line, you can add or remove side padding "
"by checking or unchecking the respective menu item and choose between a "
"custom or automatic column width. Automatic width adjusts the width of all "
"columns once to display the longest item in the column completely, except "
"for the <guilabel>Name</guilabel> column where the extension is replaced by "
"<quote>...</quote>"
msgstr ""
"Veerupäise kontekstimenüüs saab valida veeru kohandatud või automaatse "
"laiuse. Automaatse laiuse korral kohandatakse veergude laiust nii, et veeru "
"kõige pikem element oleks täielikult nähtaval, välja arvatud juhul, kui tegu "
"on veeruga <guilabel>Nimi</guilabel>, kus laiendi asemel näidatakse "
"<quote>...</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:358
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The order of columns can be changed by drag and drop of column headers, "
"except for the <guilabel>Name</guilabel> header, which is always the first "
"column in this view."
msgstr ""
"Veergude järjekorda võib muuta veerupäiseid lohistades, välja arvatud veeru "
"<guilabel>Nimi</guilabel> korral, mis on selles vaates alati esimene."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:361
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The details view allows you to view the current folder in a tree-like "
#| "fashion if <link linkend=\"preferences-dialog-viewmodes-details\"> "
#| "<guilabel>Expandable folders</guilabel></link> are enabled: Each "
#| "subfolder of the current folder can be <quote>expanded</quote> or "
#| "<quote>collapsed</quote> by clicking on the <guiicon>+</guiicon> or "
#| "<guiicon>-</guiicon> icon next to it."
msgid ""
"The details view allows you to view the current folder in a tree-like "
"fashion if <link linkend=\"preferences-dialog-viewmodes-details\"> "
"<guilabel>Expandable folders</guilabel></link> are enabled: Each subfolder "
"of the current folder can be <quote>expanded</quote> or <quote>collapsed</"
"quote> by clicking on the <guiicon>></guiicon> or <guiicon>v</guiicon> icon "
"next to it."
msgstr ""
"Üksikasjade vaade võimaldab näha aktiivset kataloogi puukujulisena, kui "
"lubatud on <link linkend=\"preferences-dialog-viewmodes-details\"> "
"<guilabel>laiendatavad kataloogid</guilabel></link>, ning iga alamkataloogi "
"saab <quote>laiendada</quote> ehk avada, kui klõpsata selle juures oleval "
"<guiicon>+</guiicon> või <guiicon>-</guiicon> ikoonil."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:372
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Grouped View</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Rühmitatud vaade</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:378
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Grouped View</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Rühmitatud vaade</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:380
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All view modes support grouping by the sort type selected in "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Sort by</guisubmenu></"
"menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"Kõik vaaterežiimid toetavad rühmitamist sorteerimistüübi järgi, mis on "
"valitud <menuchoice><guimenu>Vaade</guimenu><guisubmenu>Sorteerimine</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice> abil"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:389
#, no-c-format
msgid "Information in the View"
msgstr "Teave vaates"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:390
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In all view modes &dolphin; shows at least an icon and a name for each item. "
"Using <guisubmenu>Additional Information</guisubmenu> in the <guimenu>View</"
"guimenu> menu or the context menu of the header in <guilabel>Details</"
"guilabel> mode, you can select more information for each item to be shown:"
msgstr ""
"Kõigis vaaterežiimides näitab &dolphin; vähemalt iga elemendi ikooni ja "
"nime. Menüü <guimenu>Vaade</guimenu> alamenüüga <guisubmenu>Lisateave</"
"guisubmenu> või päise kontekstimenüüga <guilabel>üksikasjade</guilabel> "
"režiimi korral saab lasta elementide juures näidata rohkem teavet."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:397
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Size</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Date</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Type</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Rating</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Tags</guimenuitem> or <guimenuitem>Comment</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Suurus</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Kuupäev</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Tüüp</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Hinnang</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Sildid</guimenuitem> või <guimenuitem>Kommentaar</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:403
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Depending on the file type, additionally, sorting criteria can be selected:"
msgstr "Sõltuvalt failitüübist saab lisaks valida sortimiskriteeriumeid:"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:405
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenuitem>Document</guimenuitem>: Number of words and lines"
msgstr "<guimenuitem>Dokument</guimenuitem>: sõnade ja ridade arv"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:406
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenuitem>Image</guimenuitem>: Size and orientation"
msgstr "<guimenuitem>Pilt</guimenuitem>: suurus ja orientatsioon"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:407
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenuitem>Audio</guimenuitem>: Artist, album, duration and track"
msgstr "<guimenuitem>Heli</guimenuitem>: esitaja, album, kestus ja rada"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:411
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guisubmenu>Other</guisubmenu> submenu allows you to select "
"<guimenuitem>Path</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Link Destination</"
"guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Copied From</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Permissions</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Owner</guimenuitem> or "
"<guimenuitem>User Group</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Alammenüü <guisubmenu>Muu</guisubmenu> pakub samuti lisateavet: "
"<guimenuitem>Asukoht</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Lingi sihtkoht</"
"guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Kopeeritud asukohast</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Õigused</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Omanik</guimenuitem> või "
"<guimenuitem>Kasutaja grupp</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:421
#, no-c-format
msgid "Preview"
msgstr "Eelvaatlus"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:423
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If <guibutton>Preview</guibutton> is enabled, the icons are based on the "
"actual file or folder contents; &eg; for images a scaled down preview of the "
"image is shown."
msgstr ""
"Kui lubatud on <guibutton>eelvaatlus</guibutton>, väljendavad ikoonid "
"otseselt aktiivse faili või kataloogi sisu, näiteks piltide puhul näidatakse "
"skaleeritult pilti ennast."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:432
#, no-c-format
msgid "Split"
msgstr "Poolitamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:434
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If <guibutton>Split</guibutton> is clicked, two views are shown which can "
"display the contents of different folders. This can be convenient for moving "
"or copying files."
msgstr ""
"Kui klõpsata nupule <guibutton>Poolita</guibutton>, kuvatakse kaht vaadet, "
"milles võib lasta näidata eri katalooge. See on eriti mugav näiteks failide "
"liigutamise või kopeerimise korral."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:445
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selecting Items in the View"
msgstr "Vaate elementide valimine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:447
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are several ways to select items in the view. Once a group of items is "
"selected, all actions, such as <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Cut</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>, <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, "
"<menuchoice><guimenuitem>Move to Trash</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, and drag "
"and drop operations, affect all selected items."
msgstr ""
"Vaates saab elemente valida mitmel moel. Kui valitud on mitu elementi, "
"mõjutavad sellised käsud, nagu <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Lõika</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>, <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Kopeeri</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, "
"<menuchoice><guimenuitem>Viska prügikasti</guimenuitem></menuchoice> ning "
"lohistamistoiminguid kõiki valitud elemente."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:457
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selecting Items Using the Mouse"
msgstr "Elementide valimine hiirega"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:461
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can press the &LMB; somewhere in the view and draw a rectangle around a "
"group of items before releasing the button. This will select all items in "
"the rectangle and clear the previous selection. If the &Shift; key is "
"pressed during the selection process, the previous selection is kept."
msgstr ""
"Soovi korral võib ükspuha kus vaates klõpsata &HVNga; ning lohistada enne "
"nupu vabastamist ristküliku elementide ümber. Sellega valitakse "
"ristkülikusse jäävad elemendid ning tühistatakse mis tahes varasem valik. "
"Kui valimise ajal hoida all klahvi &Shift;, jääb püsima ka varasem valik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:468
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the &Ctrl; key is pressed while an item is clicked with the &LMB;, the "
"selection state of this item is toggled. If the &Ctrl; key is pressed while "
"a rectangle is drawn around a group of items as described above, the "
"selection state of all items in the rectangle will be toggled."
msgstr ""
"Kui elemendil &HVNga; klõpsamise ajal hoida all klahvi &Ctrl;, muutub "
"elemendi valikuolek. Kui klahvi &Ctrl; hoida all ülal kirjeldatud ristküliku "
"joonistamise ajal elementide ümber, muutub kõigi ristkülikusse jäävate "
"elementide valikuolek."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:475
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the &Shift; key is pressed while an item is clicked with the &LMB;, all "
"items between the previous current item and the clicked item will be "
"selected."
msgstr ""
"Kui elemendil &HVNga; klõpsamise ajal hoida all klahvi &Shift;, valitakse "
"kõik elemendid eelmise aktiivse elemendi ja klõpsatud elemendi vahel"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:480
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If <guilabel>Show selection marker</guilabel> is enabled in the <link "
"linkend=\"preferences-dialog-general-behavior\"><quote>Behavior</quote> tab "
"of the <guilabel>General</guilabel> section of the settings</link>, a small "
"<guiicon>+</guiicon> or <guiicon>-</guiicon> button appears in the top left "
"corner of the item which is currently hovered over with the mouse. Clicking "
"this sign selects or deselects the item, respectively."
msgstr ""
"Kui seadistustedialoogi <link linkend=\"preferences-dialog-general-behavior"
"\"><guilabel>üldiste</guilabel> seadistuste kaardil <quote>Käitumine</"
"quote></link> on sisse lülitatud valik <guilabel>Valiku lülitamisvõimaluse "
"näitamine</guilabel>, ilmub elemendi, mille kohal hiir parajasti viibib, "
"ülemisse vasakusse nurka väike <guiicon>+</guiicon> või <guiicon>-</"
"guiicon>. Märgil klõpsates element vastavalt kas valitakse või tühistatakse "
"selle valimine."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:494
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selecting Items Using the Keyboard"
msgstr "Elementide valimine klaviatuuri abil"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:498
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If an arrow key, <keycap>Page Up</keycap>, <keycap>Page Down</keycap>, "
"<keycap>Home</keycap>, or <keycap>End</keycap> is pressed, the new current "
"item is selected, and the previous selection is cleared."
msgstr ""
"Kui vajutada nooleklahvi või klahve <keycap>Page Up</keycap>, <keycap>Page "
"Down</keycap>, <keycap>Home</keycap> või <keycap>End</keycap>, valitakse uus "
"aktiivne element ning varasem valik tühistatakse."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:504
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the &Ctrl; key is held while one of the above keys is pressed, the "
"selection remains unchanged."
msgstr ""
"Kui mõne mainitud klahvi vajutamise ajal hoida all klahvi &Ctrl;, jääb "
"varasem valik alles."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:509
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the &Shift; key is held while one of the above keys is pressed, all items "
"between the previous current item and the new current item will be selected."
msgstr ""
"Kui mõne mainitud klahvi vajutamise ajal hoida all klahvi &Shift;, valitakse "
"kõik elemendid varasema aktiivse elemendi ja uue aktiivse elemendi vahel."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:514
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keysym>Space</keysym></keycombo> is "
"pressed, the selection state of the current item is toggled."
msgstr ""
"Klahvikombinatsiooni <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keysym>tühikuklahv</"
"keysym></keycombo> vajutamisel muutub aktiivse elemendi valikuolek."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:519
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo> selects all "
"items in the view."
msgstr ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo> valib vaate "
"kõik elemendid."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:524
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo> "
"toggles the selection state of all items in the view."
msgstr ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo> "
"lülitab vaate kõigi elementide valikuolekut."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:529
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select a file or folder by typing the first few letters of its name and the "
"first matching item is selected. To clear the selection and cancel the "
"keyboard search press &Esc; or wait longer than the timeout of 1 second."
msgstr ""
"Faili või kataloogi saab valida, kui kirjutada selle nime esimesed tähed. "
"Sel juhul valitakse kohe esimene sobiv element. Valiku puhastamiseks ja "
"otsingu katkestamiseks vajuta &Esc; või oota üle sekundi."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:547
#, no-c-format
msgid "Location Bar"
msgstr "Asukohariba"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:549
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The location bar, which can be found above &dolphin;'s view, displays the "
"path to the current folder. The location bar has two modes."
msgstr ""
"&dolphin;i vaate kohal paiknev asukohariba näitab aktiivse kataloogi "
"asukohta. Asukoharibal on kaks režiimi."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:555
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bread Crumb Mode"
msgstr "Leivaraasukese režiim"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:557
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <quote>bread crumb</quote> mode, which is the default, each folder "
"name in the path to the current folder is a button which can be clicked to "
"quickly open that folder. Moreover, clicking the <quote>&gt;</quote> sign to "
"the right of a folder opens a menu which allows you to quickly open a "
"subfolder of that folder."
msgstr ""
"<quote>Leivaraasukese</quote> režiimis, mis on ka vaikimisi režiim. on iga "
"aktiivsele asukohale viitavas kirjes olev kataloog tegelikult nupp, millele "
"klõpsates saab otsekohe vastavasse kataloogi liikuda. Kui aga klõpsata "
"kataloogist paremale jäävale märgile <quote>&gt;</quote>, avaneb menüü, mis "
"võimaldab kiiresti avada kataloogi alamkataloogi."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:565
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the location bar in bread crumb mode"
msgstr "Asukohariba leivaraasukese režiimis"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:571
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Location bar in bread crumb mode.</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Asukohariba leivaraasukese režiimis.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:573
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Location bar in bread crumb mode.</para>"
msgstr "<para>Asukohariba leivaraasukese režiimis.</para>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:580
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editable Mode"
msgstr "Redigeeritav režiim"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:582
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When in bread crumb mode, clicking in the gray area to the right of the path "
"with the &LMB; switches the location bar to <quote>editable</quote> mode, in "
"which the path can be edited using the keyboard. To switch back to bread "
"crumb mode, click the check mark at the right of the location bar with the "
"&LMB;."
msgstr ""
"Kui klõpsata leivaraasukese režiimis viibides &HVNga; asukohast paremale "
"jäävale hallile alale, lülitub asukohariba <quote>redigeeritavasse</quote> "
"režiimi, mille puhul asukohta saab redigeerida klaviatuuri abil. Tagasi "
"leivaraasukese režiimi pääsemiseks klõpsa &HVNga; asukoharibast paremal "
"asuvale linnukesele."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:590
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the location bar in editable mode"
msgstr "Asukohariba redigeeritavas režiimis"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:596
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Location bar in editable mode.</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Asukohariba redigeeritavas režiimis.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:598
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Location bar in editable mode.</para>"
msgstr "<para>Asukohariba redigeeritavas režiimis.</para>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:603
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using Kioslaves"
msgstr "KIO moodulite kasutamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:605
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the location bar is empty in editable mode, a drop down box appears in "
"front of the bar listing all available kioslaves on your system. Kioslaves "
"are programs built into &kde; which add support for many different protocols "
"to &dolphin; and other &kde; applications."
msgstr ""
"Kui asukohariba on redigeeritavas režiimis tühi, ilmub riba ette hüpikmenüü, "
"milles on näha kõik süsteemis saada olevad KIO moodulid. Viimased on &kde;-"
"sse sisse ehitatud programmid, mis toetavad &dolphin;i ja teiste &kde; "
"rakenduste tarbeks mitmesuguseid protokolle."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:610
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "For example with the <quote>fish</quote> kioslave &dolphin; can be used "
#| "to manage files and folders on a remote host that is accessible via "
#| "<acronym>SSH</acronym>. To do this you would type <userinput>fish://"
#| "username@remotehost</userinput> into the location bar. Similar remote "
#| "file management can be done on remote hosts accessible via the &FTP;, "
#| "NFS, SFTP, SMB (CIFS) or webdav protocols."
msgid ""
"For example with the <quote>fish</quote> kioslave &dolphin; can be used to "
"manage files and folders on a remote host that is accessible via "
"<acronym>SSH</acronym>. To do this you would type <userinput>fish://"
"username@remotehost</userinput> into the location bar. Similar remote file "
"management can be done on remote hosts accessible via the &FTP;, &NFS;, "
"SFTP, &SMB; (&CIFS;) or webdav protocols."
msgstr ""
"Näiteks <quote>fish'i</quote> KIO mooduliga saab &dolphin;it kasutada "
"failide ja kataloogide haldamiseks mõnes võrgumasinas, millele pääseb ligi "
"<acronym>SSH</acronym> vahendusel. Selleks tuleb kirjutada asukoharibale "
"<userinput>fish://kasutajanimi@võrgumasin</userinput>. Samamoodi saab mujal "
"asuvates masinates faile hallata &FTP;, NFS, SFTP, SMB (CIFS) või WebDAV-i "
"protokolli abil."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:616
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "It is also possible to use the kioslaves drop down list to access "
#| "&systemsettings;, fonts, trash, other programs and devices attached to "
#| "your computer. See the drop down list for the full list of capabilities "
#| "available from kioslaves on your system."
msgid ""
"It is also possible to use the kioslaves drop down box to access "
"&systemsettings;, fonts, trash, other programs and devices attached to your "
"computer. See the drop down box for the full list of capabilities available "
"from kioslaves on your system."
msgstr ""
"Samuti saab hüpikmenüüst pakutavate KIO moodulitega ligi pääseda Süsteemi "
"seadistustele, fontidele, prügikastile ja arvutiga ühendatud seadmetele. "
"Uuri hüpikmenüüd lähemalt, et teada saada, milliseid võimalusi süsteemsed "
"KIO moodulid sulle pakuvad."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:621
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the list of kioslaves"
msgstr "KIO moodulite loendi pilt"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:627
#, no-c-format
msgid "Location bar showing list of available kioslaves."
msgstr "Asukohariba saadaolevate KIO moodulite loendiga"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:629
#, no-c-format
msgid "List of available kioslaves."
msgstr "Saadaolevate KIO moodulite loend."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:637
#, no-c-format
msgid "Places and Context"
msgstr "Asukohad ja kontekst"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:639
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the <guilabel>Places</guilabel> panel is hidden; in both modes an "
"additional icon in front of the path is displayed. This icon can be clicked "
"with the &LMB; to open a menu which offers quick access to <quote>places</"
"quote> and storage media. See the <link linkend=\"places-panel\">section "
"about the Places Panel</link> for details."
msgstr ""
"Kui <guilabel>asukohtade</guilabel> paneel on peidetud, näidatakse mõlemas "
"režiimis asukoha ees lisaikooni. Ikoonile &HVNga; klõpsates avaneb menüü, "
"mis võimaldab kiiret ligipääsu <quote>asukohtadele</quote> ja salvestitele. "
"Asukohtade paneelist kõneleb lähemalt <link linkend=\"places-panel\">vastav "
"osa</link>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:647
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Location bar with Places icon</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Asukohariba asukohtade ikooniga</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:653
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Location bar with Places icon</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Asukohariba asukohtade ikooniga</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:658
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The context menu of the location bar offers actions to switch between the "
"modes and to copy and paste the path using the clipboard. Check the last "
"option in this context menu to display either the full path starting with "
"the root folder of the file system or to display the path starting with the "
"current places entry."
msgstr ""
"Asukohariba kontekstimenüü võimaldab lülituda režiimide vahel ning kopeerida "
"ja asetada lõikepuhvri vahendusel. Kontekstimenüü viimase valikuga saab "
"lasta näidata kas täielikku arukohta, alustades failisüsteemi "
"juurkataloogist, või asukohta, mis algab aktiivsest asukohakirjest."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:665
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Location bar context menu</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Asukohariba kontekstimenüü</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:671
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Location bar context menu</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Asukohariba kontekstimenüü</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:681
#, no-c-format
msgid "Panels"
msgstr "Paneelid"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:683
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&dolphin; allows a number of panels to be placed next to the view. These "
#| "can be enabled in <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Panels</"
#| "guisubmenu></menuchoice>. By unlocking the panels and clicking and "
#| "dragging a panel title, the panel can be moved to a different position, "
#| "even outside the window."
msgid ""
"&dolphin; allows a number of panels to be placed next to the view. These can "
"be enabled in <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Show Panels</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice>. By unlocking the panels and clicking and dragging "
"a panel title, the panel can be moved to a different position, even outside "
"the window."
msgstr ""
"&dolphin; võimaldab vaate kõrvale seada mitu paneeli. Neid saab lubada "
"menüükäsuga <menuchoice><guimenu>Vaade</guimenu><guisubmenu>Paneelid</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice>. Seejärel saab paneele, kui nad lahti lukustada ja "
"paneeli tiitlist lohistada, viia mõnda muusse asukohta, isegi väljapoole "
"akent."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:691
#, no-c-format
msgid "Places"
msgstr "Asukohad"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:695
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Places</guilabel> panel is located at the left of the window "
"by default. The <guilabel>Places</guilabel> panel shows any locations you "
"have bookmarked. It also shows any disk or media attached to the computer, "
"recently accessed items and allows you to search for certain type of files. "
"The order of these entries can be changed by drag and drop."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Asukohtade</guilabel> paneel asub vaikimisi akna vasakus servas. "
"<guilabel>Asukohtade</guilabel> paneel näitab kõiki järjehoidjatesse lisatud "
"asukohti. Samuti näitab see arvutiga ühendatud kettaid ja andmekandjaid ning "
"võrgus ligipääsetavaid kohti ja laseb otsida teatavat tüüpi faile. Nende "
"kirjete järjekorda saab muuta lohistades."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:702
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The easiest way to add a folder to the <guilabel>Places</guilabel> panel is "
"to drag it and drop it in the panel. Moreover, you can click inside the "
"panel with the &RMB; and choose <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Add Entry...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> from the context menu. The first procedure creates "
"a system wide bookmark, the second procedure can be used to add the current "
"path of the location bar or any desired folder or device. A dialog opens "
"where label, location and icon can be edited and the usage of this entry can "
"be restricted to &dolphin;."
msgstr ""
"Lihtsaim viis kataloogi <guilabel>asukohtade</guilabel> paneelile lisada on "
"see sinna lohistada. Lisaks võib klõpsata paneelil &HPNga; ja valida "
"kontekstimenüüst <menuchoice><guimenuitem>Lisa kirje...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> Esimese viisiga luuakse süsteemne järjehoidja, teise viisiga  "
"saab lisada asukohariba hetkeasukoha või mis tahes kataloogi või seadme. "
"Ilmub dialoog, kus saab muuta nime, asukohta ja ikooni ning piirata kirje "
"kasutamist ainult &dolphin;iga."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:712
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A &RMB; click opens the context menu to edit, add, hide or remove entries "
"and change the icon size to one of the predefined values or lock/unlock the "
"panels."
msgstr ""
"Klõps &HPNga; avab konktekstimenüü, mis võimaldab kirjeid muuta, lisada, "
"peita või eemaldada, muuta ikooni suuruse vastavaks mõnele valmisväärtusele "
"ning paneele lukustada või nende lukustust eemaldada."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:715
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The context menu has an action to open the entry in a new tab. Devices can "
"be unmounted using the context menu."
msgstr ""
"Kontekstimenüüs on ka võimalus avada kirje uuel kaardil. Samuti saab "
"kontekstimenüüga seadmeid lahutada."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:721
#, no-c-format
msgid "Information"
msgstr "Teave"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:723
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Information</guilabel> panel shows extended information about "
"the selected items(s) or about the current folder or the file which is "
"currently hovered over with the mouse, including size, type, and date of "
"last modification. It also features a large preview of the selected item and "
"allows you to assign a rating, tags, and comments to it."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Teabe</guilabel>paneel näitab täpsemat teavet valitud elementide "
"või aktiivse kataloogi või faili kohta, mille kohal parajasti hiirekursor "
"viibib, sealhulgas selle suurust, tüüpi ja viimase muutmise aega. Samuti "
"näeb seal valitud faili suuremat eelvaatlust ning saab faili hinnata ja "
"sellele silte või kommentaare lisada."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:734
#, no-c-format
msgid "Folders"
msgstr "Kataloogid"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:736
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Folders</guilabel> panel shows a tree view structure of the "
"file system. It only shows folders. Clicking a folder with the &LMB; opens "
"this folder in the &dolphin; view."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Kataloogi</guilabel>paneel näitab failisüsteemi puuvaatena. See "
"näitab ainult katalooge. Kataloogil &HVNga; klõpsamisel näitab &dolphin; "
"selle sisu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:741
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <guilabel>Limit to Home Directory</guilabel> to hide all folders from "
"the tree view except your <guilabel>Home</guilabel>."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:747
#, no-c-format
msgid "Terminal"
msgstr "Terminal"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:749
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This panel contains a terminal. The terminal will open at the folder "
"currently shown in the &dolphin; view. Changing the folder in the active "
"&dolphin; view will update the working folder of the terminal. Changing the "
"directory in the terminal will update the working folder in the &dolphin; "
"view. The terminal only works with local media."
msgstr ""
"See paneel sisaldab terminali. Terminal avatakse kataloogis, mis on &dolphin;"
"i vaates parajasti aktiivne. Kataloogi muutmine &dolphin;i aktiivses vaates "
"muudab ka terminali töökataloogi. Kataloogi muutmine terminalis värskendab "
"ka töökataloogi &dolphin;i vaates. Terminal saab kasutada ainult kohalikke "
"andmekandjaid."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:762
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quick Tips"
msgstr "Kiirsoovitused"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:764
#, no-c-format
msgid "The following are a number of tips to save time when using &dolphin;."
msgstr ""
"Järgnevalt toome ära mõned soovitused, mille järgimine aitab &dolphin;iga "
"töötades aega kokku hoida."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:769
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quick Bookmarking"
msgstr "Kiire järjehoidjate lisamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:771
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To quickly create a bookmark in the <guilabel>Places</guilabel> panel for "
"the current folder, &RMB; click in the work space and click "
"<menuchoice><guimenuitem>Add to Places</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in the "
"context menu."
msgstr ""
"Aktiivse kataloogi järjehoidja kiireks lisamiseks <guilabel>Asukohtade</"
"guilabel> paneelile klõpsa töötsoonis &HPNga; ja vali kontekstimenüüst "
"<menuchoice><guimenuitem>Lisa asukohtadesse</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:778
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The corresponding menu item visibility can be toggled via the <link linkend="
"\"preferences-dialog-context-menu\">&dolphin; context menu settings</link>."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:787
#, no-c-format
msgid "Filtering Files"
msgstr "Failide filtreerimine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:789
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&dolphin; is capable of filtering files, &ie; showing only those items in "
"the view whose name contains a given text. For example, if you wish to show "
"only the <acronym>MP3</acronym> files within a folder, you could filter for "
"<quote>.mp3</quote>. This would then filter out all files whose name does "
"not contain <quote>.mp3</quote>."
msgstr ""
"&dolphin; võib filtreerida faile. s.t. näidata vaates ainult neid faile, mis "
"vastavad sisestatud tekstile. Kui näiteks kasutaja soovib filtreerida kõik "
"kataloogis asuvad <acronym>MP3</acronym>-failid, saab neid filtreerida "
"stringiga <quote>.mp3</quote>. Sel juhul kõrvaldatakse vaatest kõik failid, "
"mille nimes ei esine osist <quote>.mp3</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:796
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To filter files, first enable the filter bar, either by pressing "
#| "<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>I</keycap></keycombo> or via the "
#| "menu: <menuchoice> <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Filter Bar</"
#| "guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. You can then enter the text to be filtered "
#| "for in the filter bar. The filter bar can be disabled either by pressing "
#| "&Esc;, or with a &LMB; click on the <guiicon>Hide Filter Bar</guiicon> "
#| "icon."
msgid ""
"To filter files, first enable the filter bar, either by pressing <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>I</keycap></keycombo> or via the menu: "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Filter...</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice>. You can then enter the text to be filtered for in the filter "
"bar. The filter bar can be disabled either by pressing &Esc;, or with a "
"&LMB; click on the <guiicon>Hide Filter Bar</guiicon> icon."
msgstr ""
"Failide filtreerimiseks tuleb kõigepealt sisse lülitada filtririba. Selle "
"avamiseks tuleb vajutada <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>I</"
"keycap></keycombo> või valida menüükäsk <menuchoice> <guimenu>Tööriistad</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Filtririba näitamine</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. "
"Seejärel saab filtriribale sisestada teksti, mille järgi filtreeritakse. "
"Filtririba peitmiseks tuleb vajutada &Esc; või klõpsata &HVNga; ikoonil "
"<guiicon>Peida filtririba</guiicon>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:807
#, no-c-format
msgid "Finding Files and Searching in Files"
msgstr "Failide otsimine ja failides otsimine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:810
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&dolphin; is capable of searching for files and for content in files. If "
#| "<keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo> is "
#| "pressed or <menuchoice> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Find...</"
#| "guimenuitem> </menuchoice> is used, the <guilabel>Find</guilabel> bar "
#| "will open already set up to search for files within the current folder "
#| "and any sub-folders. Start to type into the find input box and the search "
#| "starts immediately."
msgid ""
"&dolphin; is capable of searching for files and for content in files. If "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo> is pressed "
"or <menuchoice> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Search...</guimenuitem> "
"</menuchoice> is used, the <guilabel>Search</guilabel> bar will open already "
"set up to search for files within the current folder and any sub-folders. "
"Start to type into the find input box and the search starts immediately."
msgstr ""
"&dolphin; võib nii faile üles otsida kui ka otsida failide sisu. Kui "
"vajutada <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo> või "
"valida <menuchoice><guimenu>Redigeerimine</guimenu><guimenuitem>Otsi...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, avatakse <guilabel>otsingu</guilabel>riba, mis on "
"valmis kohe otsima aktiivses kataloogis ja selle kõigis alamkataloogides. "
"Hakka sisendkasti kirjutama ning otsing käivitub aega viitmata."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:817
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Search files and for content in files</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Failide otsimine ja failides otsimine</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:823
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Search files and for content in files</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Failide otsimine ja failides otsimine</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:825
#, no-c-format
msgid "&dolphin; searching files and for content in files."
msgstr "&dolphin; faile ja failide sisu otsimas."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:829
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The search is case insensitive, and does not require surrounding wildcards "
"(<userinput>*foo*</userinput> and <userinput>foo</userinput> are "
"equivalent), but you can use wildcards inside the search term. <userinput>*</"
"userinput> will match zero or more characters, <userinput>?</userinput> only "
"one single character."
msgstr ""
"Otsing on tõstutundetu, see tähendab ei arvesta suur- ja väiketähtede "
"erinevust, ega nõua metamärke (<userinput>*jura*</userinput> ja "
"<userinput>jura</userinput> on täpselt võrdsed), kuid samas võib metamärke "
"kasutada otsingusõna sees. <userinput>*</userinput> vastab nullile või "
"enamale märgile, <userinput>?</userinput> aga ainult üheleainsale märgile."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:833
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This feature can be used with running Baloo services; without these services "
"a KIOSlave is launched to provide the search results."
msgstr ""
"Seda võib kasutada koostöös töötavate Baloo teenustega; ilma nendeta "
"käivitatakse otsingutulemuste saamiseks KIO moodul."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:835
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The option from <guilabel>Everywhere</guilabel> with activated Baloo "
"services searches in all indexed folders, without Baloo this option starts "
"the search from the user's <replaceable>Home</replaceable> folder."
msgstr ""
"Valiku <guilabel>Kõikjal</guilabel> kasutamisel otsitakse juhul, kui Baloo "
"teenused on aktiivsed, kõigist indekseeritud kataloogidest; ilma Baloota "
"alustatakse otsinguga kasutaja <replaceable>kodu</replaceable>kataloogist."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:839
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Search with More Options</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Rohkemate võimalustega otsimine</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:845
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Search with More Options</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Rohkemate võimalustega otsimine</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:847
#, no-c-format
msgid "&dolphin; searching with More Options."
msgstr "&dolphin;i rohkemate võimalustega otsing."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:851
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Use the <guilabel>More Options</guilabel> button to extend the "
#| "<guilabel>Find</guilabel> bar. This provides a very comfortable way for "
#| "the user to shrink the number of search results."
msgid ""
"Use the <guilabel>More Options</guilabel> button to extend the "
"<guilabel>Search</guilabel> bar. This provides a very comfortable way for "
"the user to shrink the number of search results."
msgstr ""
"Nupuga <guilabel>Rohkem valikuid</guilabel> saab <guilabel>otsingu</"
"guilabel>riba laiendada. See võimaldab väga käepäraselt vähendada "
"otsingutulemuste arvu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:855
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To start a search select one or more file types (<guilabel>Documents</"
#| "guilabel>, <guilabel>Audio</guilabel>, <guilabel>Video</guilabel>, "
#| "<guilabel>Images</guilabel>), a time period and rating"
msgid ""
"To start a search select one or more file types (<guilabel>Documents</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Audio</guilabel>, <guilabel>Video</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Images</guilabel>), a time period, rating, and tag, if you have "
"defined any via <userinput>tag:<replaceable>foo</replaceable></userinput> in "
"the input box."
msgstr ""
"Otsingu alustamiseks vali üks või enam failitüüpi (<guilabel>Dokumendid</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Heli</guilabel>, <guilabel>Video</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Pildid</guilabel>), ajavahemik ja hinnang."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:860
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If the menubar is hidden, all its actions are available from the "
#| "<guibutton>Control</guibutton> button."
msgid ""
"It is possible to clear selection using the <guibutton>Clear Selection</"
"guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Kui menüüriba on peidetud, saab kõiki selle toiminguid kasutada nupu "
"<guibutton>Juhtimine</guibutton> alt."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:862
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Alternatively you can use these options in the <guilabel>Places</guilabel> "
"panel together with the <guilabel>Filter</guilabel> bar to find files using "
"Baloo or limit the search to files matching the filter expression."
msgstr ""
"Alternatiivina võib samu võimalusi kasutada <guilabel>asukohtade</guilabel> "
"paneelil koos <guilabel>filtri</guilabel>ribaga, et leida faile Baloo abil "
"või piirata otsingut failidega, mis sobivat filtris määratud stringile."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:866
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the Save icon to save a search to the <guilabel>Search For</guilabel> "
"section in the <guilabel>Places</guilabel> panel to quickly access it again "
"in the future."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:870
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <guilabel>More Search Tools</guilabel> drop-down list to select "
"other search tools than Baloo."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:876
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mounting Storage Media"
msgstr "Andmekandjate ühendamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:878
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A quick way to mount Storage Media is to click on the device in the "
"<guilabel>Places</guilabel> panel. This will mount and open the device in "
"&dolphin;."
msgstr ""
"Kõige kiirem viis andmekandja ühendamiseks on klõpsamine seadmel "
"<guilabel>Asukohtade</guilabel> paneelil. See ühendab seadme ja avab selle "
"&dolphin;is."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:886
#, no-c-format
msgid "Undo Actions"
msgstr "Tagasivõtmistoimingud"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:888
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&dolphin; is capable of undoing changes you have made to files. For example "
"if you moved a file to the Trash, &dolphin; can undo this and move it back "
"to its original location. To undo an action, press <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo> or select <menuchoice> <guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Undo: (action name)</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> in the "
"menu, &eg; <guimenuitem>Undo: Rename</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"&dolphin; võib tagasi võtta toimingud, mida kasutaja failidega sooritas. Kui "
"näiteks kasutaja viskas faili prügikasti, võib &dolphin; toimingu tühistada "
"ja liigutada faili tagasi kataloogi, kus see varem paiknes. Toimingut saab "
"tühistada menüükäsuga <menuchoice> <guimenu>Redigeerimine</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Võta tagasi: [toimingu nimi]</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> (&eg; "
"<guimenuitem>Võta tagasi: Nimeta ümber</guimenuitem> või vajutades <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:899
#, no-c-format
msgid "Renaming A Batch Of Files"
msgstr "Failide hulgi ümbernimetamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:900
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&dolphin; is capable of renaming a number of files at the same time. Each "
"file will have the file name specified, including a number, &eg;, Image1."
"jpg, Image2.jpg, Image3.jpg. This can be useful, &eg;, for pictures taken "
"with a digital camera."
msgstr ""
"&dolphin; võib korraga ümber nimetada ka palju faile. Igale failile antakse "
"määratud nimi, millele järgneb arv vastavalt sellele, kui palju faile "
"ümbernimetamiseks valiti, &eg; Pilt1.jpg, Pilt2.jpg, Pilt3.jpg. See on "
"kasulik näiteks siis, kui sul on hulk helifaile, mida tahad nummerdada "
"vastavalt radadele, või digitaalkaamerast hangitud fotosid."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:906
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you wish to rename a batch of files, first select the files to be "
"renamed. This can be done by pressing the &LMB; and drawing a rectangle "
"around the files to be renamed before releasing it, or by holding &Ctrl; and "
"clicking each file to be renamed (see <link linkend=\"selection\">Selecting "
"Items in the View</link> for more details on item selection). Then open the "
"batch-rename dialog by pressing <keycap>F2</keycap> or via the File menu: "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Rename...</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"Kui soovid korraga ümber nimetada mitu faili, tuleb need kõigepealt valida. "
"Selleks tuleb kas lohistada hiirega ümber nimetatavate failide või hoida all "
"klahvi &Ctrl; ja klõpsata kõigile vajalikele failidele (täpsemalt kõneleb "
"failide valimisest osa <link linkend=\"selection\">Vaate elementide "
"valimine</link>). Seejärel tuleb avada hulgi ümbernimetamise dialoog, mida "
"saab teha kiirklahviga <keycap>F2</keycap> või menüükäsuga "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Fail</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nimeta ümber...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:916
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Then enter the name you wish to give the files. The # character must be "
"present within the name. The files will then be renamed, where the "
"<userinput>#</userinput> character is replaced by a different consecutive "
"number for each file."
msgstr ""
"Nüüd tuleb sisestada nimi, mida kasutaja tahab failidele anda. Nimes peab "
"esinema ka märk <userinput>#</userinput> - kui märki # ei esine, tekib viga, "
"sest just see näitab, et iga faili puhul tuleb kasutada järjest suurimat "
"arvu. Seejärel nimetatakse failid ümber, lisades antud failinimele arvu "
"vastavalt sellele, kui palju on ümbernimetatavaid faile."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:922
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If all file extensions in your selection are different, the name of all "
"files can be changed without using a <userinput>#</userinput> placeholder "
"while preserving the file extensions. This is &eg; useful to rename a video "
"file and all associated subtitle files, which have the same filename, but "
"different extensions."
msgstr ""
"Kui sinu valiku failide laiendid on erinevad, saab kõigi failide nime muuta "
"ka ilma kohatäitjata <userinput>#</userinput>, säilitades faililaiendid. See "
"on kasulik näiteks videofaili ja sellega seotud subtiitrifailide nime "
"muutmisel, millisel juhul failinimi on sama, aga laiend erinev."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:930
#, no-c-format
msgid "Comparing A Selection Of Files or Folders"
msgstr "Valitud failide või kataloogide võrdlemine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:932
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the &kompare; application is installed, you can use it to see the "
"differences between two files or folders."
msgstr ""
"Kui paigaldatud on rakendus &kompare;, saab selle abil näha kahe faili või "
"kataloogi vahelisi erinevusi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:937
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"First select the two files or folders to be compared. Then launch the "
"&kompare; application via the Tools menu: <menuchoice> <guimenu>Tools</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Compare Files</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. &kompare; "
"will then open showing the differences between the files or folders."
msgstr ""
"Kõigepealt tuleb valida vajalikud failid või kataloogid. Seejärel tuleb "
"käivitada rakendus &kompare; menüükäsuga <menuchoice><guimenu>Tööriistad</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Failide võrdlemine</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Siis "
"avatakse &kompare;, mis näitab failide või kataloogide erinevusi."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:950
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring &dolphin;"
msgstr "&dolphin;i seadistamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:952
#, no-c-format
msgid "&dolphin; distinguishes two different kinds of settings:"
msgstr "&dolphin; teeb vahet kaht laadi seadistustel:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:957
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Settings which affect the general behavior of &dolphin;. These can be "
"configured using the <link linkend=\"preferences-dialog\">Preferences "
"Dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Seadistused, mis puudutavad &dolphin;i üldist käitumist. Neid saab "
"seadistada <link linkend=\"preferences-dialog\">seadistustedialoogis</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:962
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Settings which determine how the contents of a folder are displayed in "
#| "&dolphin;. These settings are called <link linkend=\"view-properties"
#| "\">View Properties</link> and can be controlled with toolbar buttons, via "
#| "the <guimenu>View</guimenu> menu, and with the <link linkend=\"view-"
#| "properties-dialog\">View Properties Dialog</link>. In the default "
#| "configuration, the view properties are remembered for each folder, but "
#| "&dolphin; can also be configured to use common view properties for all "
#| "folders in the <link linkend=\"preferences-dialog-general-behavior"
#| "\"><quote>General</quote> section of the settings</link>."
msgid ""
"Settings which determine how the contents of a folder are displayed in "
"&dolphin;. These settings are called <link linkend=\"view-properties\">View "
"Display Styles</link> and can be controlled with toolbar buttons, via the "
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> menu, and with the <link linkend=\"view-properties-"
"dialog\">View Display Style dialog</link>. In the default configuration, all "
"folders use the same display style, but &dolphin; can also be configured to "
"remember each folder's display style separately in the <link linkend="
"\"preferences-dialog-general-behavior\"><quote>General</quote> section of "
"the settings</link>."
msgstr ""
"Seadistused, mis määravad, kuidas kuvatakse &dolphin;is kataloogi sisu. Neid "
"nimetatakse <link linkend=\"view-properties\">vaate omadusteks</link> ning "
"nende muutmine on võimalik tööriistariba nuppudega, menüüs <guimenu>Vaade</"
"guimenu> ja <link linkend=\"view-properties-dialog\">vaate omaduste "
"dialoogis</link>. Vaikimisi seadistuste korral jäetakse vaate omadused "
"meelde iga kataloogi kohta eraldi, kuid &dolphin;i võib panna kasutama ka "
"ühiseid vaate omadusi kõigile kataloogidele. Seda saab teha "
"seadistustedialoogi <link linkend=\"preferences-dialog-general-behavior"
"\"><quote>üldiste</quote> seadistuste osas</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:978
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &dolphin; Preferences Dialog"
msgstr "&dolphin;i seadistustedialoog"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:979
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Preferences Dialog is opened via <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Configure &dolphin;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in the menu "
"in &dolphin;'s main window. The settings are divided into several groups "
"which can be accessed by clicking the corresponding icon on the left of the "
"dialog."
msgstr ""
"Seadistustedialoogi saab avada &dolphin;i peaaknas menüükäsuga "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Seadistused</guimenu> <guimenuitem>&dolphin;i "
"seadistamine...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> Seadistused on jagatud mitmesse "
"rühma, millele pääseb ligi klõpsuga vastavale ikoonile dialoogi vasakus "
"servas."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:986
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All settings except for the <guilabel>Startup</guilabel> page and the "
"<guilabel>Status Bar</guilabel> tab on the <guilabel>General</guilabel> page "
"are shared with &konqueror; in filemanager mode."
msgstr ""
"Kõik seadistused, välja arvatud kaardil <guilabel>Käivitamine</guilabel> ja "
"kaardi <guilabel>Üldine</guilabel> alamkaardil <guilabel>Olekuriba</"
"guilabel>, on ühised failihalduri režiimis kasutatava &konqueror;iga."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:991
#, no-c-format
msgid "General"
msgstr "Üldine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:993
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This group contains settings which control the general behavior of "
"&dolphin;. The group is divided further into four subgroups which can be "
"accessed using the tab bar at the top."
msgstr ""
"See rühm sisaldab seadistusi, mis mõjutavad &dolphin;i üldist käitumist. "
"Rühm jaguneb neljaks allrühmaks, millele pääseb ligi ülal asuva sakiriba "
"abil."

#. Tag: screeninfo
