#| msgid ""
#| "<guilabel>Split View Mode</guilabel> controls if the <link linkend="
#| "\"dolphin-view\">&dolphin; view</link> is split on startup or not."
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Begin in split view mode</guilabel> controls if the <link linkend="
"\"dolphin-view\">&dolphin; view</link> is split on startup or not for new "
"windows."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Vaaterežiimi poolitamine</guilabel> määrab, kas <link linkend="
"\"dolphin-view\">&dolphin;i vaade</link> on käivitamisel poolitatud või "
"mitte."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1186
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Show filter bar</guilabel> controls if the filter bar is shown on "
"startup or not. See the <link linkend=\"filter-files\">section on the filter "
"bar</link> for details."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Filtririba näitamine</guilabel> määrab, kas käivitamisel "
"näidatakse filtririba. Täpsemalt kõneleb sellest <link linkend=\"filter-files"
"\">filtririba käsitlev osa</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1192
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<guilabel>Editable location bar</guilabel> controls if the location bar "
#| "is in editable mode on startup. The bread crumb mode of the location bar "
#| "is used otherwise. See the <link linkend=\"location-bar\">section about "
#| "the location bar</link> for details about the two modes."
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Make location bar editable</guilabel> controls if the location bar "
"is in editable mode on startup. The bread crumb mode of the location bar is "
"used otherwise. See the <link linkend=\"location-bar\">section about the "
"location bar</link> for details about the two modes."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Redigeeritav asukohariba</guilabel> määrab, kas asukohariba on "
"käivitamisel redigeeritavas režiimis. Vastasel juhul kasutatakse asukohariba "
"leivaraasukese režiimi. Täpsemalt kõneleb neist kahest režiimist <link "
"linkend=\"location-bar\">asukohariba tutvustav osa</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1199
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Open new folders in tabs</guilabel> controls whether &dolphin; "
"should open a new folder in a new tab of the current instance when called "
"externally. If not enabled, the new folders will be opened in new instances "
"of &dolphin;. By default this option is enabled."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1203
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If <guilabel>Show full path inside location bar</guilabel> is enabled, the "
"full path of the current location is shown in the bread crumb mode of the "
"location bar. Otherwise, a shortened version of the path is shown if it "
"begins with the path of one of the places in the <guilabel>Places</guilabel> "
"panel."
msgstr ""
"Kui märgitud on <guilabel>Täieliku asukoha näitamine asukoharibal</"
"guilabel>, näidatakse asukohariba leivaraasukese režiimis aktiivset asukohta "
"täielikult. Vastasel juhul näidatakse asukohta lühendatult, kui see peaks "
"algama mõne paneelil <guilabel>Asukohad</guilabel> leiduva asukohaga."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1210
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Show full path in title bar</guilabel> makes it easy to "
"distinguish between files or folders with the same name in different folders."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1224
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This group contains settings which control the behavior of &dolphin;'s view "
"modes. The three view modes (Icons, Compact, and Details) are accessible via "
"the tab bar at the top."
msgstr ""
"Selles rühmas on seadistused, mis määravad &dolphin;i vaaterežiimide "
"käitumise. Kolme vaaterežiimi (ikoonid, kompaktne, üksikasjad) seadistused "
"on kättesaadavad ülal asuva kaardiriba vahendusel."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1230
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the Icons View settings in &dolphin;'s preferences dialog"
msgstr "&dolphin;i seadistustedialoogi ikoonivaate seadistused"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1236
#, no-c-format
msgid "View Modes Settings."
msgstr "Vaaterežiimide seadistused."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1238
#, no-c-format
msgid "View Modes Settings in &dolphin;'s Preferences Dialog."
msgstr "&dolphin;i seadistustedialoogi vaaterežiimide seadistused."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1245
#, no-c-format
msgid "Common settings for all view modes"
msgstr "Kõigi vaaterežiimide ühised seadistused"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1247
#, no-c-format
msgid "All three view modes have some common settings:"
msgstr "Kõigil kolmel vaaterežiimil on teatavad ühised omadused:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1252
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sliders which control the size of the icons. The <guilabel>Default</"
"guilabel> or <guilabel>Preview</guilabel> sizes are used if previews are "
"disabled or enabled, respectively. Note that the icon size can be changed "
"easily with the zoom slider in the status bar if the corresponding option is "
"enabled in the <link linkend=\"preferences-dialog-general-statusbar"
"\"><quote>General</quote> section of the settings</link>."
msgstr ""
"Ikoonide suurust muutvad liugurid. Suurus <guilabel>Vaikimisi</guilabel> või "
"<guilabel>Eelvaatlus</guilabel> võetakse kasutusele siis, kui eelvaatlus on "
"vastavalt keelatud või lubatud. Pane tähele, et ikoonide suurust saab "
"hõlpsalt muuta olekuriba suurendusliuguriga, kui vastav valik on sisse "
"lülitatud <link linkend=\"preferences-dialog-general-statusbar"
"\">seadistustedialoogi kaardil <quote>Üldine</quote></link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1261
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A setting for the font used in the view mode: either the system font or a "
"custom font can be chosen."
msgstr ""
"Vaaterežiimis kasutatav font: kas süsteemne või kohandatud, enda valitud "
"font."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1267
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The other settings in the <guilabel>Text</guilabel> section which apply to "
"only one of the view modes are discussed below."
msgstr ""
"Allpool tuleb juttu teistest sektsiooni <guilabel>Tekst</guilabel> "
"omadustest, mis käivad ainult konkreetse vaaterežiimi kohta"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1275
#, no-c-format
msgid "Icons"
msgstr "Ikoonid"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1278
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Width</guilabel> controls the minimum width that is reserved for "
"the text of a file item."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Laius</guilabel> määrab minimaalse laiuse, mis eraldatakse faili "
"tekstile."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1282
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Maximum lines</guilabel> means maximum number of text lines below "
"the icon."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Maksimaalne ridade arv</guilabel> tähendab tekstiridade "
"maksimaalset arvu ikooni all."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1290
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compact"
msgstr "Kompaktne"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1293
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Maximum width</guilabel> controls the maximum width that is "
"reserved for the text of a file item."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Maksimaalne laius</guilabel> määrab maksimaalse laiuse, mis "
"eraldatakse faili tekstile."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1302
#, no-c-format
msgid "Details"
msgstr "Üksikasjad"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1305
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Expandable folders</guilabel> determines whether any folders that "
"have subfolders are displayed in a tree view, where the sub items can be "
"expanded by &LMB; clicking the <guiicon>&gt;</guiicon> icon and collapsed by "
"clicking the <guiicon>v</guiicon> icon."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Laiendatavad kataloogid</guilabel>: kui see on sisse lülitatud, "
"näidatakse alamkataloogidega katalooge puuna, kus alamelemente saab avada "
"või sulgeda klõpsuga ikoonile <guibutton>&gt;</guibutton> või <guibutton>v</"
"guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1310
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Folder size</guilabel> allows defining the property to use for "
"sorting folders by their size. It is possible to sort folders by number of "
"items by choosing <guilabel>Show number of items</guilabel> or by the size "
"of the contents by choosing <guilabel>Show size of contents</guilabel>. The "
"recursion level can be limited, which can be useful to constrain unneeded "
"iterations in deep folder structures or on slow file systems. It is also "
"possible to disable displaying folder size by choosing <guilabel>Show no "
"size</guilabel> (which might improve performance in rare cases, however "
"impacts other features like sorting)."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1316
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Date style</guilabel> option can be used to configure the mode "
"to display dates in &dolphin;. It is possible to choose between "
"<guilabel>Relative</guilabel> (&eg;, <quote>Yesterday, 3:00pm</quote>) or "
"<guilabel>Absolute</guilabel> (&eg;, <quote>2020-12-23 15:00</quote>)."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1327
#, no-c-format
msgid "Navigation"
msgstr "Liikumine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1329
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This group contains settings which control how navigation in the folder "
"structure and in archives works."
msgstr ""
"See rühm sisaldab seadistusi, mis määravad, kuidas toimub liikumine "
"kataloogistruktuuris ja arhiivides."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1334
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the Navigation settings in &dolphin;'s preferences dialog"
msgstr "&dolphin;i seadistustedialoogi liikumisseadistused"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1340
#, no-c-format
msgid "Navigation Settings."
msgstr "Liikumisseadistused."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1342
#, no-c-format
msgid "Navigation Settings in &dolphin;'s Preferences Dialog."
msgstr "&dolphin;i seadistustedialoogi liikumisseadistused."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1348
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The option to open items with a single or double mouse click is a system "
#| "wide setting and can be changed in the &systemsettings; in the "
#| "<menuchoice><guimenu>Input Devices</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Mouse</"
#| "guimenuitem></menuchoice> module."
msgid ""
"The option to open items with a single or double mouse click is a system "
"wide setting and can be changed in the &systemsettings; in the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Workspace</guimenu> <guimenuitem>General Behavior</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> module."
msgstr ""
"Valik, kas avada elemente hiire ühekordse või topeltklõpsuga, on süsteemne "
"seadistus ja seda saab muuta ka Süsteemi seadistuste moodulis "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Sisendseadmed</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Hiir</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1354
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Archives will be opened inside &dolphin;, and not in an external "
"application, if <guilabel>Open Archives as folder</guilabel> is enabled."
msgstr ""
"Arhiive saab avada ka &dolphin;is, mitte välises rakenduses, kui ära märkida "
"valik <guilabel>Arhiivide avamine kataloogina</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1359
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If <guilabel>Open folders during drag operations</guilabel> is enabled, "
"dragging an item with the mouse and hovering over a folder with it for a "
"short time will open that folder. This allows you to move or copy items "
"quickly to folders which are several levels deeper in the folder hierarchy."
msgstr ""
"Kui märgitud on <guilabel>Kataloogide avamine lohistamisel</guilabel>, "
"avatakse elemendi lohistamisel hiirega ning hiirekursori jätmisel mõneks "
"ajaks kataloogi kohale see kataloog. Nii saab kiiresti liigutada või "
"kopeerida elemente kataloogidesse, mis asuvad kataloogihierarhias mitu "
"tasandit sügavamal."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1373
#, no-c-format
msgid "Services"
msgstr "Teenused"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1375
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This group offers a selection of services that can be shown in the "
"<guisubmenu>Actions</guisubmenu> submenu of &dolphin;'s context menu which "
"appears when clicking a file or folder with the &RMB;."
msgstr ""
"See rühm sisaldab teenuseid, mida näeb failil või kataloogil &HPNga; "
"klõpsamisel avaneva &dolphin;i kontekstimenüü alammenüüs "
"<guisubmenu>Toimingud</guisubmenu>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1382
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Screenshot of the Services settings in &dolphin;'s preferences dialog"
msgid ""
"Screenshot of the Services Menu settings in &dolphin;'s preferences dialog"
msgstr "&dolphin;i seadistustedialoogi teenuste seadistused"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1388
#, no-c-format
msgid "Services Settings."
msgstr "Teenuste seadistused."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1390
#, no-c-format
msgid "Services Settings in &dolphin;'s Preferences Dialog."
msgstr "&dolphin;i seadistustedialoogi teenuste seadistused."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1394
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using the <guibutton>Download New Services</guibutton> you can fetch "
"additional services for the context menu."
msgstr ""
"Nupu <guibutton>Laadi alla uusi teenuseid</guibutton> abil saab hankida "
"täiendavaid teenuseid, mida kontekstimenüüs näidata."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1398
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have installed &dolphin;'s plugins for <guilabel>Bazaar</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Mercurial</guilabel>, <guilabel>Git</guilabel> or "
"<guilabel>Subversion</guilabel> from the kdesdk module these services are "
"shown in the list. If these plugins are enabled and you enter a folder which "
"is under version control, the version state (locally changed, up to date "
"&etc;) is indicated by icons and you have additional entries in the context "
"menu like commit, update, add, remove &etc;"
msgstr ""
"Kui oled paigaldanud &dolphin;i pluginad <guilabel>Bazaar</guilabel>i, "
"<guilabel>Mercurial</guilabel>i, <guilabel>Git</guilabel>i või "
"<guilabel>Subversion</guilabel>i tarbeks, mida pakub kdesdk moodul, näeb ka "
"neid nimekirjas. Kui need pluginad on sisse lülitatud ja sa liigud "
"kataloogi, kus asuvad versioonihaldussüsteemi paigutatud failid, siis "
"näidatakse ikoonidega versioonide olekut (kohalikult muudetud, värske jne.) "
"ning kontekstimenüüsse tekivad uued kirjed sissekandmiseks, uuendamiseks, "
"lisamiseks, eemaldamiseks jne."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1407
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Changes whether items are sorted by <guimenuitem>Name</guimenuitem>, "
#| "<guimenuitem>Size</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Date</guimenuitem>, "
#| "<guimenuitem>Permissions</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Owner</guimenuitem>, "
